info.description:
This is the API documentation for the PDU OSS Deployment Tracking Tool. This should provide you with all the support you need to consume the Rest API.
NOTE: Certain REST calls require user authentication.
For information on how to authenticate REST calls, click here: https://eteamspace.internal.ericsson.com/display/CITT/DTT+-+Authenticating+REST+Calls
